tm-cT5vgYmQW3XDyTGDUI/edit</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">未來&amp;過去活動</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://kazemai.github.io/fgo-vz/event_history.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkazemai.github.io%2Ffgo-vz%2Fevent_history.html&d=WTx8YifNbAy2WvdCmHyJUDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ffd371f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://kazemai.github.io/fgo-vz/event_history.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Servant一覽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://kazemai.github.io/fgo-vz/servant.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkazemai.github.io%2Ffgo-vz%2Fservant.html&d=WTx8YifNbAy2WvdCmHyJUDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5fe38c7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://kazemai.github.io/fgo-vz/servant.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">素材計算器</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://tsukimiyamiyabi.github.io/fgo-skillitem/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftsukimiyamiyabi.github.io%2Ffgo-skillitem%2Findex.html&d=WTx8YifNbAy2WvdCmHyJUDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3c5ab1ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://tsukimiyamiyabi.github.io/fgo-skillitem/index.html</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">溫馨提示</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">呢個POST係主要討論FGO繁中版。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">其他Server就可免則免。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">如果想入坑嘅巴打推薦去淘寶search「FGO台服」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">入面有好多唔同組合嘅石頭號，可以自己睇下邊個啱再決定點起手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">同埋講還講最好唔好講幾多抽中</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">考慮下抽唔到嘅巴打感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">最後希望大家和平討論，唔好成日發動PVP mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ORmAbYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORmAbYD.jpg&h=2c4a315b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71GAL5A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71GAL5A.png&h=6afd5e88&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/ec5e480950074388714bb2ee517960448a4590bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2Fec5e480950074388714bb2ee517960448a4590bd.png&h=994a7f25&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e68803e59b882b1834c18895017c26e9b3e01a3f","tid":936862,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"開個post都咁閪耐"},{"pid":"083a793490ff05b4ef43408ef2a02b3fcfd26ce6","tid":936862,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"同埋點解今次都係29..."},{"pid":"d31d8b0ca7611b9c2e24315d1e824a3cd69c7557","tid":936862,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:56:45.000Z","msg":"開個post都咁閪耐仲要開錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79bc72a94f19898273170bc0dcd173a38eaf519","tid":936862,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"個Heading睇咗做準備射到莉莉絲有BB <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ca690c6f6b985921c743a690314377a23edc4e","tid":936862,"uid":32256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79bc72a94f19898273170bc0dcd173a38eaf519","tid":936862,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"